16:42.760 --> 16:44.330
Oh, whoa, easy, easy, easy.

16:44.440 --> 16:46.681
No static, bro.

16:46.760 --> 16:49.491
I got us another Excelsior.

16:50.480 --> 16:53.689
Yeah. It's in a derelict foundry
on the outside of town.

16:53.760 --> 16:57.162
