here all day,

17:02.240 --> 17:03.890
or we could go in there
and just do it.

17:04.000 --> 17:05.650
Then why are we still here?

17:05.960 --> 17:07.484
Let's go do the shit!

17:14.800 --> 17:17.007
Goddamn!

17:17.640 --> 17:19.961
Just the smell of the
metal makes me hard.

17:20.440 --> 17:22.727
That the same one
as the pizza place?

17:22.800 --> 17:24.290
Well, I ain't the manufacturer.

17:25.079 --> 17:26.286
But it looks close enough.

17:26.800 --> 17:29.371
Looks like it's in pretty good
shape, too, for being abandoned.

17:29.440 --> 17:31.329
Hell, an A-bomb
could go off,

17:32.080 --> 17:34.162
this baby would still be
standing in the rubble.

17:34.280 --> 17:36.408
Well, Wiz, that doesn't exactly
inspire a lot of confidence

17:36.480 --> 17:38.448
