get inside this thing.

17:38.520 --> 17:40.966
Dude, I get through time locks,

17:41.360 --> 17:43.886
magnetic seals,
shit you wouldn't understand

17:44.000 --> 17:45.650
even if I drew you a diagram.

17:45.720 --> 17:47.370
This old pile of tungsten,

17:47.440 --> 17:48.805
this is just pure brute force.

17:49.560 --> 17:50.686
Drill and kill.

17:51.160 --> 17:52.366
You want to see what I can do?

17:54.040 --> 17:55.405
Next time, make it tough.

17:55.840 --> 17:57.524
One job at a time, Wiz.

17:58.000 --> 17:59.126
Okay.

18:02.000 --> 18:03.843
Give me your cellphones.

18:14.520 --> 18:17.649
Ava, come over here and
meet the classiest jeweler

18:17.720 --> 18:19.324
this side of the Mississippi.

18:19.400 --> 18:21.448
Oh, so nice to
meet you, Winston.

18:21.520 --> 18:23.522
Beautiful pieces you have here.

18:23.800 --> 18:26.883
I feel like I should've worn my
sunglasses, all the sparkling around.

18:27.000 --> 18:28.206
Okay, he gets it.

18:28.520 --> 18:30.284
Oh! Speaking of diamonds,

18:30.360 --> 18:31.441
may I?

18:31.520 --> 18:32.681
Of course.

18:32.760 --> 18:34.250
The tennis bracelet.

18:34.320 --> 18:36.368
Oh, I love that.
Hmm.

18:38.000 --> 18:39.365
There we are.

18:39.440 --> 18:42.091
Oh, my goodness,
what a sight.

18:43.040 --> 18:45.008
Winston, would you
do me a favor?

18:45.080 --> 18:47.048
Would you let Ava
try on something pretty

18:47.120 --> 18:48.884
to just give her
a little thrill?

18:48.960 --> 18:50.200
Surely.

18:52.120 --> 18:53.963
Is there anything

18:54.040 --> 18:55.166
that strikes your fancy?

18:55.560 --> 18:57.130
Oh, the whole store does.

18:57.240 --> 18:59.004
One thing prettier
than the next.

18:59.720 --> 19:02.326
Well, now, let's see.

19:03.400 --> 19:05.767
How about these?

19:07.080 --> 19:11.051
That's okay. I feel funny even
picking up something that expensive.

19:11.120 --> 19:12.804
Afraid I might drop it
or something.

19:12.920 --> 19:14.888
No, they won't bite.
Here.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.121
Okay.

19:17.440 --> 19:18.487
Oh.

19:19.240 --> 19:20.241
Oh, my.

19:20.920 --> 19:22.684
I look like a movie star.

19:22.760 --> 19:24.603
You do.
Matches your eyes.

19:25.360 --> 19:26.964
Thank you so much.

19:27.040 --> 19:28.087
Of course...
Shit!

19:28.560 --> 19:30.240
