19:30.560 --> 19:32.927
No problem, ma'am.
Happens all the time.

19:37.440 --> 19:39.044
There we go.

19:39.880 --> 19:41.480
Is there anything else
you'd like to see?

19:41.720 --> 19:44.371
Uh... I think
that's enough for me.

19:44.440 --> 19:47.364
Winston, I'm gonna pass on
the tennis bracelet for now.

19:47.440 --> 19:48.646
Maybe next time.

19:48.720 --> 19:49.926
So good to see you.

19:50.040 --> 19:51.883
It's always a pleasure.
All right.

19:57.720 --> 19:58.926
Whoo-hoo.

19:59.000 --> 20:00.729
My heart's beating
like a jackrabbit!

20:00.800 --> 20:03.280
Just run with it, honey.
It's all part of the fun.

20:03.360 --> 20:04.771
That place was covered
in cameras.

20:04.880 --> 20:06.370
What if he decides to call the...
Oh, Winston

20:06.440 --> 20:08.647
is not gonna do jack shit.

20:08.720 --> 20:11.644
He's too afraid I still have
the juice to have him killed,

20:11.720 --> 20:13.643
him or one of his
mongoloid sons.

20:14.640 --> 20:16.881
When Grady was at his peak,

20:16.960 --> 20:18.724
I had a charge account
at that store

20:18.800 --> 20:20.643
and a dozen others just like it.

20:21.600 --> 20:22.840
Shit...

20:23.400 --> 20:25.721
Winston used to greet me
at that door with champagne.

20:25.800 --> 20:27.882
Now he locks it on me.

20:27.960 --> 20:29.724
Screw him.

20:40.080 --> 20:42.003
When you gonna tell me? What?

20:42.080 --> 20:43.650
The story of Mrs. Hutchins?

20:43.760 --> 20:45.091
Was she the teacher who cared?

20:45.160 --> 20:47.447
She watered little Raylan
so he could blossom?

20:47.520 --> 20:49.249
I hated her.
She hated English.

20:49.320 --> 20:51.004
Nearly turned me off of books.

20:51.080 --> 20:54.050
Only thing she taught me was
don't do a job just for money.

20:54.120 --> 20:56.327
Well, now you're doing
what you love.

20:56.440 --> 20:57.965
Miss Hutchins, American hero.

20:58.240 --> 20:59.640
How much do you want
to bet that she

20:59.680 --> 21:01.842
and Mr. Hutchins didn't die
peacefully in their sleep?

21:01.920 --> 21:04.048
Oh, but it's such
a nice thought.

21:04.440 --> 21:06.249
It's how I want to go.

21:06.320 --> 21:07.321
I'm kidding.

21:07.400 --> 21:09.971
I want Sigourney Weaver to
choke me out with her thighs.

21:10.080 --> 21:12.526
You understand I'm
formulating a theory here?

21:13.360 --> 21:17.649
You think Markham's "Coadjutors"
made it look that way?

21:17.960 --> 21:19.610
Mmm-hmm. Made an offer
on the property,

21:19.680 --> 21:21.808
got refused.
Good theory, right?

21:21.880 --> 21:24.884
Seeing as how Harlan isn't much
in the way of farmland, yeah.

21:25.520 --> 21:28.410
Those names in Calhoun's books
are probably the primo spots.

21:28.480 --> 21:31.484
Markham gets those, he can
plant a shit ton of pot crops,

21:31.600 --> 21:33.284
betting Kentucky goes legal.

21:33.360 --> 21:36.364
Which, if it does,
good for Kentucky.

21:37.280 --> 21:40.648
But if he's acting like one
of them Old West black hats

21:40.720 --> 21:43.200
forcing homesteaders
off their land,

21:44.080 --> 21:45.650
that ain't gonna stand.

21:45.720 --> 21:48.929
It's just with fire, you
could maybe prove arson.

21:49.760 --> 21:51.489
It's a failed furnace
in an old house?

21:51.560 --> 21:53.130
It's a theory.

21:53.200 --> 21:55.646
This is what you get with
a teacher's pension, uh?

21:58.240 --> 21:59.810
Congratulate me.

22:01.920 --> 22:03.081
What is that?

22:03.160 --> 22:05.766
Window's covered in plastic
and taped shut.

22:06.320 --> 22:09.688
I bet you a silver dollar
they got no next of kin,

22:09.760 --> 22:12.889
house goes up for auction,
Markham gets it for a song.

22:13.960 --> 22:15.246
Okay, then.

22:21.520 --> 22:23.602
Maui.
Maui?

22:24.560 --> 22:27.245
Where I grew up, the
mean streets of Paia.

22:28.280 --> 22:30.328
Surfed the bay every
morning before school.

22:32.120 --> 22:35.920
Wynn Duffy on a surfboard. That's
something I have a hard time picturing.

22:36.240 --> 22:38.322
I'll show you
my trophies one day.

22:38.400 --> 22:41.370
A million dollars does afford
a man a lot of sex wax.

22:41.440 --> 22:43.488
Although given
what we're about to do,

22:43.560 --> 22:44.721
I'm surprised
you ain't planning to surf

22:44.840 --> 22:46.524
somewhere far,
far away from here.

22:47.840 --> 22:49.410
That your plan?

22:49.480 --> 22:53.041
Sequester yourself in some
lost corner of the globe?

22:53.680 --> 22:55.648
You speak Farsi, do ya?

22:55.720 --> 22:56.960
Tunisian?

22:57.520 --> 22:59.966
For one thing, they speak
Arabic in Tunisia.

23:00.040 --> 23:03.089
Second, my future address
has yet to be decided.

23:03.480 --> 23:04.845
Hey, does it swing
right or left?

23:05.320 --> 23:07.049
I'm assuming you mean
the vault door?

23:07.120 --> 23:09.407
Well, I ain't talking about
your little white pee-pee.

23:09.480 --> 23:10.527
Yeah. Which way?

23:10.960 --> 23:12.041
Let's go right.

23:12.160 --> 23:13.207
And what year was it?

23:13.280 --> 23:14.441
Why?

23:14.520 --> 23:17.444
Because in 1970, Excelsior
changed their design.

23:17.520 --> 23:19.841
They started sandwiching
out the copper alloy.

23:19.960 --> 23:22.247
They were...
You know what?

23:22.320 --> 23:23.970
Never mind.
It's all good.

23:24.040 --> 23:26.327
The Wiz always has it covered.

23:29.720 --> 23:31.927
I told you assholes to leave
your cellphones in the car!

23:47.800 --> 23:49.404
Ho, ho!

23:50.000 --> 23:51.445
What up, pimps?

23:53.080 --> 23:57.847
To what do I owe these particular
splinters in my asshole today?

23:58.600 --> 24:01.046
If splinters are all you're
getting back there, Dickie,

24:01.120 --> 24:02.360
prison has treated you well.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.771
Isn't that
just like you?

24:03.840 --> 24:05.569
Isn't that just like him?

24:05.640 --> 24:10.123
To find hurtful potty mouth
humor in sexual assault.

24:10.200 --> 24:11.361
Maybe I should apologize.

24:11.440 --> 24:13.249
Maybe I should tease you
about the wheelchair.

24:13.680 --> 24:15.728
I get conflicting impulses
when I see you.

24:15.800 --> 24:17.802
Sure you lovers
don't want a conjugal?

24:18.920 --> 24:20.160
Candy? Cookies?

24:20.680 --> 24:23.126
Chocolate donuts in a box?

24:23.200 --> 24:24.281
Don't forget soda pop.

24:24.400 --> 24:25.401
And soda pop.

24:27.520 --> 24:29.648
I get it. I get it.
I see you two.

24:29.880 --> 24:32.281
This right here,
this is a, what you call it?

24:32.360 --> 24:34.522
A revelation.
This is... Yeah!

24:34.600 --> 24:38.127
This is one of them
ecstatic visions

24:38.200 --> 24:39.361
I've been having of late.

24:39.440 --> 24:42.091
All right, all right!
Here we go.

24:42.840 --> 24:44.285
Mighty spirit.

24:44.360 --> 24:45.691
Dickie Bennett,

24:46.040 --> 24:48.168
this is archangel Raylan,

24:48.960 --> 24:51.850
here to deliver unto thee

24:51.920 --> 24:55.891
a loaded up commissary in
exchange for your cooperation

24:55.960 --> 24:58.611
in a Federal Criminal
Investigation. Oh!

24:58.680 --> 25:01.160
Message received,
but I'm afraid what you ask...

25:01.240 --> 25:04.005
It's just, it's too great.

25:04.080 --> 25:05.080
It really is.

25:05.120 --> 25:07.726
I cannot see a way
to answer your call.

25:08.240 --> 25:09.480
Search your soul, numb nuts.

25:09.560 --> 25:14.009
Can you not see the Lord
herself hath damned me with...

25:15.560 --> 25:17.722
Incipient diabetes?

25:19.160 --> 25:20.207
You shitting me?

25:20.440 --> 25:21.851
Negatory.

25:21.920 --> 25:23.649
So barter the sweets.
Get what you want.

25:24.320 --> 25:26.129
There you go.

25:27.160 --> 25:30.243
I don't believe you,
you're hearing me.

25:30.320 --> 25:32.129
What I'm trying to say is,
I'll break it down here...

25:39.800 --> 25:41.609
Well, we can go the other way.

25:42.280 --> 25:44.123
Just make life
in here unpleasant.

25:44.200 --> 25:46.168
- More unpleasant.
- The threats, yes.

25:46.560 --> 25:48.324
Here they come.
Bring it on.

25:48.440 --> 25:50.886
This is my favorite part.

25:50.960 --> 25:52.803
We're upsetting you?
You want us to leave?

25:52.880 --> 25:54.405
You could just tell us
who bought your land.

25:54.480 --> 25:57.131
Records indicate
LM Consolidated.

25:57.240 --> 25:59.004
The broker's name
turned out to be a fake.

25:59.080 --> 26:01.321
Who was it wanted their
identity concealed?

26:01.400 --> 26:02.606
Yes,
you're absolutely right.

26:02.680 --> 26:05.889
I would be delighted
to tell you why I sold it.

26:06.680 --> 26:08.489
Would you like to?

26:08.560 --> 26:09.721
This ought to be good.

26:10.200 --> 26:11.690
I hope you made a tidy sum

26:11.760 --> 26:12.921
for your dumbassedness.

26:13.000 --> 26:15.526
Drove a hard bargain,
yeah, yeah.

26:15.600 --> 26:17.921
But I did I managed to.
I pushed her back.

26:18.000 --> 26:20.082
I did, and I ended up with...

26:20.160 --> 26:22.208
A tidy sum.

26:22.920 --> 26:24.160
Her?
Yeah, her.

26:24.240 --> 26:28.768
The guy behind the guy
is said to have been,

26:28.840 --> 26:30.490
after all that, a she.

26:30.960 --> 26:32.928
You follow that?

26:35.200 --> 26:38.010
She was a she?
LM Consolidated?

26:38.080 --> 26:39.241
You never met her?

26:39.320 --> 26:41.687
That's what I said the last five times.
I'll give you six.

26:44.280 --> 26:48.126
You were so hot to start a feud
with me that had long since ended,

26:48.200 --> 26:52.125
you sold your ancestral
land to Loretta McCready?

26:53.440 --> 26:54.680
Loretta?

26:57.840 --> 26:59.080
Loretta?

27:00.040 --> 27:03.123
That good land has
more to it than rich soil.

27:03.200 --> 27:05.089
It has history.

27:05.160 --> 27:07.970
And we know your desire
to build on that history,

27:08.040 --> 27:10.850
which is in line
with our desire.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.888
In short, the future.

27:14.600 --> 27:16.443
Now, the other thing
I wanted to tell you

27:16.880 --> 27:19.008
is to forget our first offer.

27:19.080 --> 27:21.003
We're now prepared
to pay you twice that

27:21.240 --> 27:22.890
to show you how committed we are

27:22.960 --> 27:25.406
to the preservation and
prosperity of this land.

27:25.960 --> 27:28.122
Well, I'll need
to think about that.

27:28.200 --> 27:32.603
Well, consider that if you
invest that money wisely,

27:32.680 --> 27:35.081
hell, you can burn
through half of it first.

27:37.080 --> 27:38.920
